      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": null,
      "message": "You don't have to define separate handlers for each distro - those handlers differ only in the command so it would suffice to parametrize it:\n\nRole defaults:\n  <keyname>:\n    RedHat:\n      <cmd_keyname>: <custom command>\n    Debian:\n      <cmd_keyname>: <custom command>\n\nhandlers/main.yml:\n\n(...)\n command: \"{{ <keyname>[ansible_os_family][<cmd_keyname>] }}\"\n(...)",
